text:
Shantanu Maheshwari, Asha Negi, Devoleena Bhattacharjee: Inside pictures of Ekta Kapoor’s Telly Calendar 2017 launch event 
We are back with our weekly Instagram roundup. We have got some really hot stuff this week – Vinny Arora – Dheeraj Dhoopar ‘s stylish honeymoon snaps, Asha Negi ‘s Paris throwback picture, Aashka Goradia ‘s stunning photo-shoot, Ekta Kaul ‘s bold avatar and Nakuul Mehta ‘s devastatingly killer looks. Here is the entire lowdown. 
Dheeraj Dhoopar and Vinny Arora’s stylish honeymoon 
Newlyweds Dheeraj Dhoopar and Vinny Arora recently went to Maldives for their honeymoon. Vinny is looking super sexy in the pictures. This is the first time when she is seen sporting bikinis.
